{"id":59102,"date":"2024-09-13T16:21:00","date_gmt":"2024-09-13T10:51:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=59102"},"modified":"2024-09-14T19:31:19","modified_gmt":"2024-09-14T14:01:19","slug":"box-bed-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/box-bed-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"8 Innovative Box Bed Designs for Compact Bedrooms"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Transform your bedroom with these innovative box bed designs that maximise storage and style.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>As cities become more congested, compact homes and apartments have become the norm. Finding unique furniture pieces to maximise storage is now a must. This is why beds with built-in storage, also known as box beds, are now one of the most sought-after trends among homeowners. This blog shall explore some unique box bed designs that add additional space and serve as stunning centrepieces in your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/master-bedroom-design-ideas\/\">master bedroom<\/a> at the same time. Let\u2019s dive in!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Latest Double Bed Designs With Box Underneath<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When you have only one bedroom for your kids and yourselves, it calls for innovation. The bunk box bed, like the one shown in the image, provides ample storage along with a queen-sized bed for parents and a single bunk for your kid, all while maintaining a sleek, contemporary look. This design integrates two large drawers beneath the bed, perfect for storing extra bedding, clothes, or other essentials. Using storage drawers as a staircase to the top bunk ensures your kid\u2019s safety and adds immense storage space for books, toys, and clothes. The yellow adds a pop of colour to the grey and white room, making this bed a perfect fit for a family room in a modern apartment.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192655\/latest-double-bed-designs-with-box.jpg\" alt=\"Latest double bed design with a box underneath is perfect for extra storage\" class=\"wp-image-59106\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192655\/latest-double-bed-designs-with-box.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192655\/latest-double-bed-designs-with-box-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192655\/latest-double-bed-designs-with-box-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192655\/latest-double-bed-designs-with-box-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Sleek designer bunk bed with hidden storage under the bed and stairs<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. Modern Box Bed Design with Hydraulic Lift<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for a modular box bed that perfectly blends with your home\u2019s existing decor and adds a ton of additional storage? Take a look at this image. This king-size bed has a hydraulic lift mechanism that offers easy access to a spacious storage area underneath, allowing you to keep your room clutter-free effortlessly. The minimalist design with a muted colour palette is ideal for a contemporary setting, where simplicity and functionality are key.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192707\/modern-box-bed-design-with-hydraulic-lift.jpg\" alt=\"A modern box bed design with a hydraulic lift adds plenty of storage\" class=\"wp-image-59107\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192707\/modern-box-bed-design-with-hydraulic-lift.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192707\/modern-box-bed-design-with-hydraulic-lift-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192707\/modern-box-bed-design-with-hydraulic-lift-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192707\/modern-box-bed-design-with-hydraulic-lift-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Stylish hydraulic box bed for a compact room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. Wooden Box Bed Design with Hidden Shoe Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Who said beds are only for sleeping? With modular solutions, you can easily add innovative storage solutions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For instance, wooden box beds like the one shown in the image combine timeless bed design with modern storage solutions, which is a must-have for any <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/small-bedroom-design-ideas\/\">compact bedroom<\/a>. This design features multiple pull-out drawers perfect for storing extra bedding or occasionally used items. The most unique part of these designs is the shoe cabinet smartly hidden into the bed&#8217;s frame. This eliminates the need for an additional shoe storage box, saving precious floor space. The rich wooden finish adds warmth and a touch of traditional elegance, making it a versatile piece that complements various interior styles.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192738\/wooden-box-bed-design.jpg\" alt=\"A wooden box bed design features multiple pull-out drawers perfect for storing extra bedding\" class=\"wp-image-59110\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192738\/wooden-box-bed-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192738\/wooden-box-bed-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192738\/wooden-box-bed-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192738\/wooden-box-bed-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A versatile wooden bed is a testament to classic elegance with durability<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. Wooden Box Diwan Bed Design With Hidden Bookcase<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Diwan beds are known for their versatility, and the box diwan bed design shown in the image exemplifies this perfectly. This piece provides ample storage space underneath that is accessible through pull-out drawers. It also features an ingeniously concealed pull-out bookcase within the headboard. It is an ideal choice for the master bedroom or guest room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192748\/wooden-box-diwan-bed-hidden-bookcase.jpg\" alt=\"A wooden box diwan bed with pull-out drawers\" class=\"wp-image-59111\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192748\/wooden-box-diwan-bed-hidden-bookcase.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192748\/wooden-box-diwan-bed-hidden-bookcase-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192748\/wooden-box-diwan-bed-hidden-bookcase-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192748\/wooden-box-diwan-bed-hidden-bookcase-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Stylish resting solution with ample hidden storage<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. Single Box Bed with Integrated Toy Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This innovative single-box bed design combines sleeping and playtime needs, making it perfect for a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/kids-bedroom-design\/\">child\u2019s room<\/a>. The bed features a large pull-out drawer for storing toys and other knick-knacks, keeping the room neat and organised. It eliminates the need to invest in storage bins, thereby saving precious floor space for your child to play. The corner setup also ensures that the bed fits snugly by the wall, ensuring your child sleeps safely.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192718\/single-box-bed.jpg\" alt=\"A single box bed includes a large pull-out drawer for storing toys\" class=\"wp-image-59108\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192718\/single-box-bed.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192718\/single-box-bed-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192718\/single-box-bed-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192718\/single-box-bed-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A smartly designed single bed is the need of every home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. All-Rounder Sunmica Box Bed Design with Lift-Up Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A perfect blend of style and functionality, this king-size sunmica box bed design offers a comprehensive storage solution with its hydraulic lift-up mechanism. This feature provides easy access to a spacious storage area beneath the mattress, ideal for storing bulky items like blankets, bedding, or seasonal clothes. The bed\u2019s sleek and modern design ensures it fits seamlessly into any <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/contemporary-bedroom-designs\/\">contemporary bedroom decor<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192728\/sunmica-box-bed-design-with-lift-up-storage.jpg\" alt=\"A sunmica box bed design with lift-up storage beneath the mattress\" class=\"wp-image-59109\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192728\/sunmica-box-bed-design-with-lift-up-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192728\/sunmica-box-bed-design-with-lift-up-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192728\/sunmica-box-bed-design-with-lift-up-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192728\/sunmica-box-bed-design-with-lift-up-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Hydraulic lift makes lifting the bed easier<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">7. Double Box Diwan Bed Design with Versatile Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The double diwan box bed design is a versatile solution for any bedroom, combining comfort with ample storage space. It features multiple pull-out drawers on both sides of the bed, perfect for storing linens, clothing, or other essentials. The diwan style adds a touch of elegance and provides additional seating space, making it a multifunctional piece of furniture that enhances the room&#8217;s aesthetics and functionality.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192643\/double-bed-with-box-design.jpg\" alt=\"A double bed with a box design has multiple pull-out drawers on both sides\" class=\"wp-image-59105\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192643\/double-bed-with-box-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192643\/double-bed-with-box-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192643\/double-bed-with-box-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192643\/double-bed-with-box-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Multiple storage drawers make this a desirable option<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">8. Multi-Compartment Box Bed with Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Take your storage game to the next level with this multi-compartment piece. Check out this box bed! Built into the base, once the bed\u2019s top frame is raised, you can easily access the additional storage underneath. This stunning design allows you to keep your room neat and organised. This multi-compartment bed is a great solution for those with limited space but don\u2019t want to sacrifice style, making it a perfect addition to any modern bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192632\/box-bed-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"A box bed with storage has multiple compartments underneath\" class=\"wp-image-59104\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192632\/box-bed-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192632\/box-bed-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192632\/box-bed-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/14192632\/box-bed-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Maximise existing space with stylish multi-compartment bed<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Box beds are a perfect blend of style and functionality in a small bedroom space, making them a popular choice for both modern and traditional interiors. Whether you\u2019re interested in the sleek look of a steel bed, the classic elegance of a wooden design, or the practicality of a hydraulic lift bed, there\u2019s a box bed to suit every taste and need. Upgrade your bedroom with these innovative designs and enjoy the perfect combination of form and function.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like this article? Check out our blog section for more such <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/\">bedroom design ideas<\/a>. If you want to transform your bedroom or home into a dreamy abode, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">book a free consultation<\/a> with us today!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQ on Box Bed Designs<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1. Can a box bed be disassembled for easy moving?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, most box beds can be disassembled, making them easier to transport.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2. Can a box bed accommodate under-bed storage?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Box beds are designed with built-in under-bed storage compartments.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. Can a box bed be used as a daybed or sofa?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, certain box bed designs, especially diwan beds, can double as a daybed or sofa.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4. How do I choose the right size box bed for my room?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Measure your room and consider the bed&#8217;s dimensions, ensuring there\u2019s enough space for easy movement.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>5. Can I customise the colour or finish of a box bed?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Many manufacturers offer customisation options, allowing you to choose the colour or finish that best suits your decor.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06164015\/91.png\"\n                    selected>\n                    +91\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+44\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/medi